Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.88,0:01:34.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Immediately go to the World of the Living\Nand check for the spirit waves
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:37.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,of the Arrancars\Nas well as the Espada.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.52,0:01:42.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, simplify the procedures\Nto execute a Gentei Kaijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.60,0:01:48.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So, in order to meet\Nthe Head Captain's demands...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.12,0:01:52.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Have one of the staff go to\Nthe World of the Living, Akon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.24,0:01:54.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:58.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very interested in\Ninvestigating the Arrancars,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.92,0:02:02.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's no guarantee that\NI'll come across an Espada
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:04.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,in the World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:08.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll set out in the winter\Nduring the showdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:10.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the research documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.99,0:02:16.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The captain probably just doesn't\Nwant to be bothered with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.88,0:02:20.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Who wants to go to\Nthe World of the Living?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.28,0:02:22.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.92,0:02:24.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a chronic illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.64,0:02:25.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yes...\N- Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:27.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.47,0:02:31.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.89,0:02:33.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubokura, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.35,0:02:38.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How unusual... You normally\Njust eat sweets and slack off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.52,0:02:40.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:42.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:49.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Someone from Squad 4 will\Nprotect and guide you on this mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:50.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.72,0:02:52.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Tsubokura, one more thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:53.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.08,0:02:57.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Give this to Third Seat Madarame.\NIt's the molars he wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:02:58.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.80,0:03:10.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the Senkaimon that\Nleads to the World of the Living...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:15.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! The day has finally come!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:18.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The World of the Living probably\Nhas a lot of sweets that we don't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:20.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'm going to stuff myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:21.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,First...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:24.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Western sweets! I believe\Nthey were called "cakes."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:26.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how sweet they are\Nand what they taste like!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:28.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.36,0:03:30.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:34.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.00,0:03:40.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:42.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Owowowow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:43.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:47.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was ordered to go with you\Nto the World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:50.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hanataro Yamada of Squad 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:53.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Rin Tsubokura of the Department\Nof Research and Development.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:56.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:03:59.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,URAHARA'S SHOP\N\N\N\N\Nwhat is this store?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.12,0:04:00.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,URAHARA'S SHOP\N\N\N\N\NThis is Urahara's Shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:05.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I come here often when I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:07.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:11.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Isn't anyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:12.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:15.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Amazing!\NThere are so many sweets!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:17.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! This looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.16,0:04:20.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't eat that without paying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:24.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubokura?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.12,0:04:27.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:32.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Tessai! It's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:35.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, for my current mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:38.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come here to research\Nbattle sites with Tsubokura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:41.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As well as simplifying Gentei Kaijo,\Neven just a little,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.72,0:04:45.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,in preparation for battle against\Nthe Arrancars and the Espada.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:49.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I've heard about that\Nfrom Captain Hitsugaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:52.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, we had a rough time\Nin the last battle
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:55.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,because the Gentei Kaijo\Nwas taking too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:59.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall show you the place\Nwhere the Arrancars appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:01.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.68,0:05:05.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayasegawa, show them the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:07.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still not convinced...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:09.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.48,0:05:14.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hitsugaya said that you\Nlooked like you had the most free time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:17.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so he was going to\Nmake you go with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:19.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Free time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:21.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:25.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why does this always\Nhappen to me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:32.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, are you finished yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:35.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I really am busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:38.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you hurry it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:43.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:47.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I've picked up a pattern!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.48,0:05:51.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take us to\Nthe next place, Ayasegawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.68,0:06:01.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's such a bother to\Nhave to walk to get around!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.60,0:06:05.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...\NI'm not very good at Flash Step.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:08.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:11.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:12.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:14.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubokura's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:16.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gotten lost now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.28,0:06:21.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:25.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!\NWe're on a mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:28.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... They were selling\Nsuch delicious-looking cakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:29.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so I ended up buying one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:30.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ended up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:36.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But how could you buy one\Nwhen you're not in a gigai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:37.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, as for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:39.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I used this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:48.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a machine that can make\Na soul look as if it's a physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:53.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have it, you can\Nbuy a cake without a gigai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:56.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.\NCan you finish up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.36,0:07:01.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:02.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:07.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A bound spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.60,0:07:13.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:17.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:20.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... We're Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:21.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:22.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:29.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem attached to this store,\Nbut it's dangerous for you to stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.28,0:07:30.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:33.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, what are you going to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:38.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hollows will come after\Na soul like you if you stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:44.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Or you'll become a Hollow\Nand attack your relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:45.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:51.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to prevent that,\Nwe're going to send you to Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:54.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:59.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There'll be trouble if you do that!\NListen to my story!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:01.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! You'll feel better soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:03.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:06.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:09.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... Won't you listen to his story?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:12.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Let's listen to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:22.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What an amazingly long chain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:28.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Bound spirits usually\Ncannot move from their spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:30.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:32.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.48,0:08:35.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Heita Momoyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:39.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a cake baker who\Nused to work at that shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:44.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was hit by a car\Nin front of the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:50.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I worked hard every day\Ntraining to make cakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:56.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't make cakes anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:08:59.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.84,0:09:04.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubokura, you're unusually\Nresponsive to talk of cake...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:08.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's troubling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:13.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...it's my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:26.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother comes to\Npray for me here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.52,0:09:30.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,every morning when\Nthe streets are still deserted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:35.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But lately, she's been getting thinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:37.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Unable to bear it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.48,0:09:40.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,my older sister and her husband\Nsuggested that she live with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:43.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Well, that's a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.08,0:09:45.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:47.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite the fact that I was training,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.84,0:09:51.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I never had my mother\Neat any of my cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:53.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.64,0:09:59.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:05.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to make a cake!\NI'll teach you how.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:06.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:09.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want my mother to eat\None of my cakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:15.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit odd, but if you make it\Nto my specifications, it's still my cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:16.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:21.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez. I never expected you to say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:22.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:23.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:27.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You just want to eat cake, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:29.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:31.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking about cakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:33.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:35.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:40.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Wow!\N- Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:45.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A first appearance!\NUrahara's Shop's kitchen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:48.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice kitchen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:49.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:53.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I consulted with Tessai\Nand remodeled it just recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:11:01.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Try not to damage anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.48,0:11:03.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:07.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I have all of your ingredients.\NFeel free to use them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:13.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's kind of odd for Ayasegawa\Nto be interested in this as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.72,0:11:15.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:19.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make a cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.04,0:11:22.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:27.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:35.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But these clothes aren't so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.32,0:11:43.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat the fresh cream harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:44.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:45.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:47.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:51.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason my egg\Nbecame mushy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:53.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.64,0:11:58.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that it needs to be\Nat body temperature!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:11:59.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:02.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll become a hot spring egg!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:04.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.00,0:12:05.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Remake it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.56,0:12:06.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.44,0:12:08.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't taste it too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:12.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:14.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:18.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too small!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:21.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:24.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you to do it\Nbecause I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.32,0:12:28.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.48,0:12:31.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we can give it to your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.16,0:12:32.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:34.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:37.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we have to taste it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.04,0:12:40.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.60,0:12:45.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If it tastes good,\Nwe'll make another one to give to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.36,0:12:48.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't eat it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:56.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time we've eaten cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:12:57.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.12,0:13:00.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have them in Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:03.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there anyone\Nwho has had cake before?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.96,0:13:05.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:09.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:11.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Zabimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:15.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:21.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you are getting a little better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:23.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Once more, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.52,0:13:25.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:31.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:34.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So you want us to see how it tastes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.52,0:13:37.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've had cake before, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:41.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know everything there is to know\Nabout the World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.60,0:13:43.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it a taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.64,0:13:44.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.52,0:13:52.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to remake it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.52,0:14:32.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I probably won't be able to\Neat a delicious cake...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.12,0:14:35.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that. Let's give it our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:47.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Momoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:50.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that his mother\Nis moving tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:55.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That means that tomorrow is the last day\Nthat she'll come to leave flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:07.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That's just right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:11.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good, too.\NThings are looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.08,0:15:16.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good. Yes. It's very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:19.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow is the last day...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.68,0:15:20.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.64,0:15:25.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make a beautiful,\Ndelicious cake for your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:29.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayasegawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:31.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.52,0:15:35.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's give it our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.96,0:15:36.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.32,0:15:42.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:46.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If it tastes good, we'll be set.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:55.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's incredibly soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:57.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel kind of happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.00,0:15:59.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's a beautiful taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:02.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:05.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for your mother to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.20,0:16:06.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:07.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:16.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:18.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:21.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends of Momoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:24.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We heard that you\Nwould be moving today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.72,0:16:31.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Thank you for looking\Nafter Heita when he was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:37.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Momoyama's cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.56,0:16:38.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:41.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, we made it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:46.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was made according to\Nthe recipe that Momoyama taught us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.08,0:16:49.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Momoyama's flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:54.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Heita's?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.08,0:17:00.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit late, but this is my cake, mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:07.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... I can't accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:08.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:10.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:14.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand cakes anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.96,0:17:17.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I see a cake,\NI always remember him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:19.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:21.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:23.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So...I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:25.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:26.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Give this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:28.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:32.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.92,0:17:35.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My cake...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:39.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted mom to eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.28,0:17:42.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.28,0:17:46.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go, mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:49.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:52.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Momoyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.04,0:17:54.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:02.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. The Spiritual Pressure\Nis attracting them...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:03.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.12,0:18:07.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A Menos Grande!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.65,0:18:08.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:14.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting worried over a Menos?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.60,0:18:15.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How unsightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:22.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:26.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumichika!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:29.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How careless of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.28,0:18:30.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:32.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me,\Nthank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.80,0:18:34.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.36,0:18:35.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:38.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Worry about yourself before worrying\Nabout others, thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.60,0:18:39.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.12,0:18:42.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down and try to\Nmaintain consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:46.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:48.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.84,0:18:51.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go, mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:55.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.40,0:18:57.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Momoyama!\NGet a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.28,0:19:07.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! It's only a Menos...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.88,0:19:11.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- What should we do?\N- Why won't you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:14.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- He's really going to become a Hollow.\N- eat my cake, mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:18.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't, Heita!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.48,0:19:24.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:25.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In this case...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:28.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.24,0:19:30.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.16,0:19:32.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:44.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Fill up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:45.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hisagomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.28,0:19:52.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Ayasegawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:55.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Bloom, Fujikujaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:11.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanataro, what was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.72,0:20:14.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my zanpakuto, Hisagomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.76,0:20:15.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.76,0:20:16.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.68,0:20:22.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hisagomaru gets to Shikai\Nby absorbing people's wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.64,0:20:24.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it shows its true power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:27.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you healed\NMomoyama's wounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:28.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.36,0:20:33.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A chest hole is a wound of the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.68,0:20:37.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't fully open yet, so I thought\Nthat I might be able to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:39.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? That's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.32,0:20:41.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:44.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:47.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.40,0:20:50.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:53.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Heita!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.08,0:20:56.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad, mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.24,0:20:58.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.52,0:21:02.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom? You can see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:05.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,When did he...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:10.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, I finally completed my cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:13.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it was true?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:18.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It got a bit smashed,\Nbut I can guarantee that it tastes good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.52,0:21:24.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's delicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.52,0:21:26.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.56,0:21:28.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Very...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.44,0:21:30.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is your cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.92,0:21:35.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Heita...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.32,0:21:40.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't ever say that it hurts\Nwhen I see a cake anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:41.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.04,0:23:22.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The machine you made that makes\Nsouls take physical form...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.19,0:23:23.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So it doesn't just work on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.69,0:23:26.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It can work on any soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.31,0:23:28.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that mean that we wouldn't\Nhave had to go through all that trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.65,0:23:30.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,if we had used it on him\Nfrom the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.79,0:23:33.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Yumichika, you're really smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.59,0:23:34.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He's no good...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.21,0:23:36.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.38,0:23:37.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Golden!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.92,0:23:39.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.57,0:23:41.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.24,0:23:43.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the data?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.36,0:23:44.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.23,0:23:48.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, did you give\NThird Seat Madarame his molars?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.84,0:23:52.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I stomped on them\Nwhen I was fighting the Menos.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.81,0:23:54.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So I did as you told me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.02,0:23:57.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I put them in a bag\Nwith a note that says that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.74,0:24:01.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,"they're molars\Nthat only idiots can't see."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.82,0:24:04.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... You really did that?!